{"text_id":207918,"tokens":["Co","litis"," is"," a"," medical"," condition"," that"," occurs"," when"," the"," large"," intestine"," becomes"," inflamed","."," It"," can"," result"," from"," an"," infection"," or"," an"," autoimmune"," response",","," and"," can"," be"," chronic"," or"," acute","."," In"," order"," to"," cure"," colitis",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," first"," understand"," what"," it"," is"," and"," its"," symptoms",".","\n","Part"," ","1",":"," Understanding"," Co","litis","\n","Learn"," what"," colitis"," is",":"," Co","litis"," is"," a"," medical"," condition"," characterized"," by"," inflammation"," of"," the"," large"," intestine",","," which"," is"," responsible"," for"," the"," absorption"," of"," water"," and"," electrolytes",".","\n","Take"," note"," of"," general"," colitis"," symptoms",":"," Symptoms"," of"," colitis"," often"," include"," abdominal"," pain",","," diarrhea",","," and"," bloody"," stool",".","\n","Seek"," medical"," attention"," immediately",":"," If"," you"," experience"," any"," of"," these"," symptoms",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," seek"," medical"," attention"," immediately",","," as"," they"," can"," indicate"," a"," serious"," condition",".","\n","Get"," checked"," for"," an"," infection",":"," Infectious"," colitis"," can"," result"," from"," any"," type"," of"," infection"," \u2014"," bacterial",","," viral",","," or"," parasitic","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," get"," checked"," for"," an"," infection"," if"," you"," suspect"," colitis",".","\n","Consider"," pseud","ome","mb","ran","ous"," colitis",":"," If"," you"," have"," taken"," antibiotics"," recently",","," you"," may"," be"," at"," risk"," for"," pseud","ome","mb","ran","ous"," colitis","."," This"," occurs"," when"," antibiotics"," kill"," too"," much"," of"," your"," beneficial"," bacteria",","," allowing"," harmful"," bacteria"," to"," take"," over",".","\n","Think"," about"," inflammatory"," bowel"," disease"," (","IB","D","):"," Ul","cer","ative"," colitis"," and"," Crohn","'","s"," disease"," are"," two"," types"," of"," IBD"," that"," can"," lead"," to"," chronic"," colitis",".","\n","Look"," for"," signs"," of"," ischemic"," colitis",":"," Is","chemic"," colitis"," can"," occur"," when"," local"," arteries"," become"," blocked",","," reducing"," blood"," flow"," to"," the"," large"," intestine",".","\n","Sus","pect"," necro","tizing"," entero","coli","tis"," (","NEC",")"," in"," newborns",":"," NEC"," is"," a"," condition"," that"," affects"," premature"," babies"," or"," those"," who"," are"," given"," formula"," instead"," of"," breast"," milk",".","\n","Part"," ","2",":"," Seeking"," Treatment"," for"," Co","litis","\n","Consult"," your"," healthcare"," provider"," about"," medicinal"," treatments",":"," There"," are"," a"," number"," of"," medications"," available"," to"," treat"," colitis",","," including"," anti","-","inflammatory"," drugs"," and"," immunosupp","ress","ants",".","\n","Consider"," antibiotic"," use",":"," Antibiotics"," may"," be"," prescribed"," to"," treat"," bacterial"," infections"," that"," cause"," colitis",".","\n","Talk"," to"," your"," doctor"," about"," biologic"," therapies",":"," Bio","logic"," therapies"," are"," treatments"," derived"," from"," biological"," material",","," such"," as"," protein",".","\n","Be"," prepared"," for"," surgery"," if"," necessary",":"," If"," other"," treatments"," fail",","," surgery"," may"," be"," necessary"," to"," treat"," colitis",".","\n","Part"," ","3",":"," Managing"," Co","litis"," Symptoms","\n","Take"," antibiotics"," for"," colitis"," resulting"," from"," a"," bacterial"," infection",":"," If"," you"," are"," diagnosed"," with"," bacterial"," gastroenter","itis"," or"," food"," poisoning",","," antibiotics"," may"," be"," prescribed",".","\n","Manage"," any"," diarrhea",":"," De","hydration",","," nausea","/","vom","iting",","," and"," fatigue"," are"," common"," concerns"," with"," diarrhea","."," Be"," sure"," to"," stay"," hydrated"," and"," rest"," as"," needed",".","\n","Avoid"," problem"," foods"," that"," might"," cause"," IBS"," flare","-","ups"," or"," worsen"," diarrhea",":"," Foods"," such"," as"," dairy",","," caffeine",","," and"," spicy"," or"," fatty"," foods"," can"," exacerbate"," symptoms",".","\n","Eat"," small"," meals",":"," Eating"," smaller",","," more"," frequent"," meals"," can"," help"," reduce"," digestive"," discomfort",".","\n","Drink"," enough"," fluids",":"," Be"," sure"," to"," drink"," plenty"," of"," fluids"," to"," stay"," hydrated"," and"," replace"," any"," fluids"," lost"," through"," diarrhea",".","\n","Ask"," your"," doctor"," about"," multi","vitamin"," use",":"," If"," your"," diet"," is"," restricted"," due"," to"," colitis",","," your"," doctor"," may"," recommend"," a"," multi","vitamin"," to"," ensure"," adequate"," nutrition",".","\n","Reduce"," your"," stress",":"," Stress"," can"," exacerbate"," symptoms"," of"," colitis","."," Try"," to"," find"," ways"," to"," manage"," stress",","," such"," as"," through"," exercise"," or"," meditation",".","\n","Avoid"," medications"," that"," could"," cause"," flare","-","ups",":"," Certain"," medications",","," such"," as"," non","ster","oidal"," anti","-","inflammatory"," drugs"," (","NSA","IDs","),"," can"," exacerbate"," symptoms"," of"," colitis",".","\n","Try"," alternative"," treatments",":"," Pro","biotics"," can"," be"," useful"," in"," promoting"," healthy"," bacteria"," in"," the"," digestive"," tract",","," helping"," to"," reduce"," inflammation"," and"," manage"," symptoms"," of"," colitis","."],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}